    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel needed for gem industry in Ratnapura under QR code soon: Minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Necessary measures will be taken for the delivery of fuel through Sri Lanka Transport Board (SLTB) depots for 4,000 gem miners in Ratnapura district who are engaged in the gem mining industry, Plantation Industries and Minister of Industries Minister Ramesh Pathirana said.",
        "He said this while addressing a special meeting between Ratnapura Miners, Gem Traders Association and Plantation Industries at Ratnapura yesterday.",
        "He also said that the Minister will take actions to introduce a program to obtain the fuel required for the gem industry from other petrol stations through QR code in collaboration with the Power and Energy Ministry. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
